posting_body: ['STUDIO / WASHER & DRYER / DISHWASHER / FITNESS CENTER / PARKING / CONCIERGE', 'Listing ID #: 211176', 'Price: $4,482', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: Studio', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Laundry', 'This luxury residence puts you in the center of an all-encompassing lifestyle.', 'Enjoy modern homes with today’s finest blend of sophisticated appointments.', 'Peace and serenity await you, while the excitement of the all the city has to offer is right at your doorstep!', 'Located in the historic West Village, you are surrounded by cobblestone streets, landmark buildings, hidden square and ivy covered facades.', 'The premier location includes easy access to galleries, cafes, great eateries and boutiques.', 'The only new rental residence built in this landmark area in more than decade.', 'Come live in this historic area where art and culture are in abundance!', 'For showings contact:', 'Adel Talebpour / The Bouklis Group / 212-961-7334 (cell) / <URL> / <URL> / <URL>', 'Adel Talebpour', 'Phone: 212-402-7855', 'Mobile: 212-961-7334', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 212-402-7855 \xa0 212-961-7334 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Adel Talebpour at 212-961-7334']
